        <span class="text-title"> 100% Lifetime Exchange </span>
      </summary>
      <p>
        Get 100% of the metal and diamond value at prevailing market rates, subject to final valuation and verification.
        Exchange value can be used to purchase new Lucira jewellery and cannot be encashed, with a ₹1,500 deduction in
        case of certificate loss.
      </p>
      <div class="design-font-div-wrapper">
        <span class="design-font"> Because your jewellery should evolve with your style, not limit it. </span>
      </div>
    </details>

