        <span class="text-title"> 15 Day Easy Moneyback </span>
      </summary>
      <p>
        Returns are accepted within 15 days for items in original condition with complete packaging. Customized pieces,
        engraved items, and loose solitaires are not eligible for return, while scheme, wallet, EMI, and international
        orders are eligible for exchange only.
      </p>
      <div class="design-font-div-wrapper">
        <span class="design-font"> Because peace of mind matters as much as sparkle. </span>
      </div>
    </details>

